<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chat Group | Mental Health App</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="chat-container">
        <h2>Discussion: Managing Anxiety in Workspaces</h2>

        <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
            <p><strong>John Doe:</strong> I find it really helpful to take short breaks during work.</p>
            <p><strong>Emma Stone:</strong> Yoga has been amazing for me. It really helps with stress.</p>
        </div>

        <form id="chatForm">
            <input type="text" id="chatInput" placeholder="Type your message..." required>
            <button type="submit">Send</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script src="../assets/js/chat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
